TopicTitle: Looking for a lost 5 Meter Docking port

Articles.Content: I had trouble after the last update so I deleted everything and started from scratch. Now, after downloading what mods I actually cared about, I have lost a 5 meter docking port.  I do not know what mod it was on and can't find it anywhere.  It was much wider than normal ports and much stronger.  It was black not stainless.  Any ideas which mod this is on?  Any ideas for stronger docking ports in general, to provide a more stable launch?

8 hours ago, ProcrastinatorSpaceDiv. said:

I have lost a 5 meter docking port. 

Get the part name from the error message / log file, and search for that string in the backup you sensibly made before you started deleting things. Alternatively, if it was part of a common mod, you might try entering it in the search box here.
